                                <td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=6189&amp;sid=d320ff74f9a296bd14f8c70653b47acf#6189"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Tue Sep 30, 2003 8:14 am<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: GRRR this guy made me mad (long pick up group story)</span></td>
                                <td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=6189&amp;sid=d320ff74f9a296bd14f8c70653b47acf"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
